Title: BI view filtering: fixed broken host and service filters
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: bi
Date: 1623155562
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

The filters <tt>Affected hosts contain</tt> and <tt>Affected by service</tt> did not correctly filter aggregations.
This lead to empty views.
